{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act42side", "eventName": "眾生行記", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "MT-1", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "聖秩", "storyInfo": "第二屆萬國峰會順利召開，從卡茲戴爾到阿戈爾，泰拉諸國無不以最高規格前來參會。但在關鍵時刻，拉特蘭城內意外發生了一起爆炸案，剛剛升任樞機的蕾繆安被委派調查此案。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "39_i14", "block": "false", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$alarmenter", "volume": 0.6, "loop": "true", "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "危機。", "x": 180.0, "y": 170.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "重複警告。", "x": 180.0, "y": 170.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n危機。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n……危機等級……評估中……", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n不可知……", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n解除鎖定。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "底層運算區域鎖定解除。", "x": 180.0, "y": 170.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n推演算力已突破上限。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n拉特蘭……爆發。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n……", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "1", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g2_laterano_cathedralhall", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_361_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，終於能喘口氣了。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#6$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_361_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這輩子都沒有說過這麼多的話，一想到明天又要再說一輩子的話……", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#7$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，要不然我們交換一下工作？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接待卡茲戴爾使節團的任務交給我，至於明天抵達的那十三座移動修道院，你來負責安置，怎麼樣？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跑來跑去對骨質疏鬆的老頭子來說太不友善了！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_361_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那倒是不用，帕特里奇昂閣下。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#6$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和我們的薩卡茲友人溝通還順利嗎？", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_361_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還不錯。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#6$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_361_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確實還有薩卡茲無法放下仇恨，比如跟隨那位維什戴爾議長的古老魂靈，只是遠遠瞥見牧首的身影就暴跳如雷。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#2$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_361_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幸好議長很識時務地把他們訓斥得啞口無言，態度好到我都要懷疑關於她的奇妙傳聞是怎麼來的了。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#6$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡茲戴爾使節團的主要發言人是那位名叫弗萊蒙特的巫妖，可惜您沒看見那場面——", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#6$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_361_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "整整三小時的外交辯論，從政治到律法，從信仰到生死，他一個人和第一廳、第六廳的十七位樞機激烈地“交換意見”……", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#2$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "結束之後，口乾舌燥的樞機們圍著甜點機狂喝芭樂汁。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#2$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣有活力的老傢伙，真是令人神往啊！", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之，結論是，卡茲戴爾認同了我們的倡議——諸王庭會重新審視傳承已久的王權，薩卡茲將在拉特蘭的協調下團結一心。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就在剛剛，我與女皇之聲也碰了面——萊塔尼亞的使節團明天清晨就會抵達聖城。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_361_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？真是稀奇。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#7$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想想兩年前，萬國峰會應者寥寥，絕大多數人都認為所謂的“拉特蘭主張”只是一紙空泛的解經。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當時，伊維格娜德女皇拒絕了我們的邀請，而這次，她主動請求參加萬國峰會。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "甚至已經沉寂許久的赫琳瑪特女皇也現身了，這次將一同到訪拉特蘭……", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_361_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊塔尼亞的誠意十足啊。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#6$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帕特里奇昂閣下，我們是否可以認為，第二屆萬國峰會已經取得了預期中的成功？", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#6$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遠超預期，薇爾麗芙樞機。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "目前為止，哥倫比亞、烏薩斯、炎國，甚至是遠海的阿戈爾……該來的都來了。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_361_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感覺像在做夢。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#2$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這只不過是拉特蘭長久發展的必然結果。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啟示中的災異已經臨近，薩米冰蓋上的黑雪、萊塔尼亞上空的罅隙，甚至衝擊海岸的狂潮，都是在呼應它必然的降臨。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "災異當頭，任何人都會渴望秩序——拉特蘭的秩序。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您說得沒錯。只不過，哪怕做了這麼久的準備，這場面也還是讓我感到……陌生。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你尚且如此，其他人就更不必說了。哪怕啟蒙時就在佈道中無數次聽過拉特蘭為應對啟示中的災異所鋪設的道路……", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真到了親自迎接它所導向的結果時，也還是會有所猶疑。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_361_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您自己呢？", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#7$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然不想倚老賣老，但到了我這個年紀，哪還有什麼猶疑的餘地呢？", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_361_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您準備退休了？", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#4$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊。我老到連仙人掌塔都嚼不動了，協助舉辦這屆峰會恐怕就是我能為拉特蘭做的最後一件事了。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_361_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閣下，我覺得這是您口味太過奇異的緣故。您說的那種……仙人掌塔，恐怕我也很難咬動。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#2$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_361_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您不會不知道，冷餐會上的仙人掌塔都是專門為您訂製的吧？畢竟拉特蘭城沒有第二個人癡迷這種怪東西了。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#6$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼可能？仙人掌塔是一個甜點鑑賞造詣極高的老朋友傾情推薦的……呃，他叫什麼呢……", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了，言歸正傳。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然還有人心存疑慮，之後將在育嬰聖堂舉辦的那場儀式就至關重要。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們需要以最有力的方式向所有人展示，拉特蘭能帶來怎樣的可能性。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瞭解。我馬上交接第七廳的工作，萬國峰會接下來的這段時間，我會前往聖堂，確保儀式順利進行。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倒也不用那麼急。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，算了。嘴上有再多抱怨，真的行動起來又都是急性子……年輕人還真是相像。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_361_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您想起了您的“小菲”吧？", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#5$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_361_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "根據任務調遣記錄——她已經回來了？", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#6$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，明天是我們的家庭聚會……希望小菲喜歡我準備的禮物。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_aircraftalarm", "volume": 0.2, "loop": "true", "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "1", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "61_g1_nurserytemplesquare", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#3$2", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "育嬰聖堂……", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#3$2"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是壯美的奇蹟。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#3$2"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-200,0", "duration": 1.5, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"maskid": "group_interclude_vertical_common", "size": "290,760", "style": 0.0, "switch": "true", "offset": "250,0", "channel": 3.0, "tsfrom": "0,1", "tsto": "1,1", "tsduration": 0.5}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "false", "pfrom": "235,0", "pto": "235,0", "name": "char_empty", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "-200,0", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第七廳樞機，蕾繆安。請說。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "-200,0", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "true", "pfrom": "235,0", "pto": "235,0", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蕾繆安樞機，儘快趕往司提望區約維塔街，調查一起潛在的爆炸案。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#14$2", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "-200,0", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "false", "pfrom": "235,0", "pto": "235,0", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帕特里奇昂閣下？我不記得今天的日程包含了這部分內容。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#14$2"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#14$2", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "-200,0", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "true", "pfrom": "235,0", "pto": "235,0", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你剛剛上任，可能還不太清楚。緊急調度可以無視任何部門的任何安排。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "-200,0", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "false", "pfrom": "235,0", "pto": "235,0", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "緊急調度……這是來自哪裡的判斷？有文件可以參考嗎？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "-200,0", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "true", "pfrom": "235,0", "pto": "235,0", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "情況緊急與否從來都是不言而喻，無需任何人來做額外的判斷。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個來歷不明的人屢次攜帶未登記的爆炸物，在沒有公證所監督的情況下出現在公共場合——", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是對拉特蘭秩序莫大的破壞。聖城千百年的寧靜，絕不能在萬國峰會期間、眾目睽睽之下，被一次非法爆炸打破。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嫌疑人剛剛被目擊在司提望區約維塔街現身，你是目前距離最近的公職人員。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請你立刻前往現場。你的輔佐官與公證所的執行者稍後會前去支援，預計將在你抵達現場後的十分鐘內到位。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#8$2", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "-200,0", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "false", "pfrom": "235,0", "pto": "235,0", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瞭解。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#8$2"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#8$2", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "-200,0", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "true", "pfrom": "235,0", "pto": "235,0", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……蕾繆安。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#8$2", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "-200,0", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "false", "pfrom": "235,0", "pto": "235,0", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有什麼情況需要我知悉？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#8$2"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#8$2", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "-200,0", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "true", "pfrom": "235,0", "pto": "235,0", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本來想祝你上任快樂的……就留到明天聚會上再說吧。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#11$2", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "-200,0", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "false", "pfrom": "235,0", "pto": "235,0", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聚會，您能到嗎？大家都知道您臨近退休反倒越來越忙，而您又……", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#11$2"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#11$2", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "-200,0", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "true", "pfrom": "235,0", "pto": "235,0", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我又偏偏永遠以公務為重？這我倒沒辦法否認。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有些老朋友的聚會一拖再拖，拖到我這個老糊塗連對方的名字都記不清楚了，也不好意思再去見面了。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但明天的聚會，我會想辦法不錯過。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "-200,0", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "false", "pfrom": "235,0", "pto": "235,0", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您辛苦了。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼我現在就動身前往約維塔街。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "clear": "true", "tsfrom": "1,1", "tsto": "0,1", "tsduration": 0.5}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "clear": "true"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#8$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_phonebutton_3", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽得到嗎？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#8$2"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#8$2", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蕾繆安？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經在育嬰聖堂這邊了，但臨時有事，就不進去了。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#14$2"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#14$2", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#11$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說什麼了嗎，我沒聽清楚欸。幹嘛那麼小聲，你也不是小氣的人吧？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#11$2"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（……你誤會了，蕾繆安。）", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（我沒事。只是現在情況特殊，我得藏起來不被人發現，沒辦法大聲說話。）", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我們直接在菲亞梅塔家的聚會上見吧。", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（好。）", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（注意安全。）", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_ringoff_long", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼~", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "60,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 0.0, "type": "bg", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "61_g4_nurseryindoor", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1802_1#1$2", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1801_1#1$2", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1802_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "肯定在這裡，雖然他壓低了聲音，但瞞不過我的耳朵！", "name": "驕傲的小孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1802_1#1$2"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1801_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用你說，我也猜到了！", "name": "倔強的小孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1801_1#1$2"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "窗簾後面沒有，柱子後面沒有……", "name": "倔強的小孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1801_1#1$2"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“這個櫃子只有半個人高，他的個子那麼高，肯定沒辦法躲進去”——他一定覺得我們會這麼想！", "name": "倔強的小孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1801_1#1$2"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1802_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "笨笨的！", "name": "驕傲的小孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1802_1#1$2"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1801_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他不笨，是我們太聰明了！", "name": "倔強的小孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1801_1#1$2"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1802_1#1$2", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "找到你囉，保育員先生！", "name": "驕傲的小孩&倔強的小孩"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#1$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧好吧，願賭服輸——今天的自由活動時間延長三十分鐘！", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#11$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1802_1#1$2", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1801_1#1$2", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好耶——！", "name": "驕傲的小孩&倔強的小孩"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1802_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "保育員先生，快帶我們玩“光環遊戲”！", "name": "驕傲的小孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1802_1#1$2"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天我要第一個鑽進奶瓶，第一個鑽出奶嘴，第一個被你抱起來，然後和你手牽手，一起迎接後面鑽出來的孩子們！", "name": "驕傲的小孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1802_1#1$2"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1785_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們啊，又纏著安多恩叔叔不放了。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1785_1#1$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們想多玩一下，沒有什麼不好。吉賽爾、洛米雅，先去啟聖大廳做準備吧，這樣我一趕到，遊戲就可以開始了，好嗎？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#11$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1802_1#1$2", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1801_1#1$2", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1785_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前輩，您從來都不會拒絕孩子們嗎？", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1785_1#1$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想必就是這樣，孩子們才如此信任您、依賴您……", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1785_1#1$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您看，幾週前他們還對這座陌生的聖堂感到無比恐懼，就連幫他們換一件衣服都還會掙扎到筋疲力盡。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1785_1#1$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在他們已經把這裡當成自己的家了……您功不可沒，安多恩前輩。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1785_1#1$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我確實沒做什麼，只是陪在他們身邊罷了。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#12$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1785_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您與牧首真的很像，就連過分謙遜這點也是。其實，有您陪在身邊，就能改變許多了。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1785_1#1$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您與牧首共同帶回聖城的那位母親，不正是因為有您的陪伴，才熬過了最困難的時候？", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1785_1#1$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還記得，負責接診的醫生離開手術室後，做的第一件事是去看自己的光環還在不在。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1785_1#1$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就連他也不能理解，一位被長槍貫穿了腹部的母親，是如何帶著孩子一起存活下來的。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1785_1#1$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "簡直堪稱奇蹟。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1785_1#1$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等到她順利分娩再讚嘆奇蹟也不遲。在此期間，我會盡我所能地繼續照顧她。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#6$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1785_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我有些理解牧首對您的看重了，安多恩前輩。由您來負責降生儀式上最重要的接生步驟，確實令人安心。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1785_1#1$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果降生儀式一切順利，育嬰聖堂就將全面投入使用，屆時，泰拉的每一位新生兒都將接受聖城的庇護與賜福。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1785_1#1$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那時，我們才算是真正創造了奇蹟，對吧？", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1785_1#1$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但願如此……但願如此。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#10$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1785_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，我不多打擾前輩了。吉賽爾和洛米雅還等著您呢。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1785_1#1$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#1$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g11_laterano_alley", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "司提望區，約維塔街"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#8$2", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真安靜啊……", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#8$2"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "頭頂光環的隊伍在街道上延伸，無人駐足，也無人喧鬧。"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告解車與甜點車從街邊駛過，偶爾有人跨出隊伍鑽進一輛告解車，其他人也只是伸手從甜點車裡接過一支冰淇淋，便繼續無聲地行進。"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寂靜無聲，井然有序，聖城拉特蘭從來都是如此。"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已到達指定位置。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正在秘密調查可疑人員，暫時沒有發現任何異常。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g11_laterano_alley", "xScale": 1.5, "yScale": 1.5, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.1, "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.1, "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_365_1#1$1", "focus": "all", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_365_1#1$1", "focus": "all", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {